    "body" : "I think you <i>might</i> come across some problems if you use <code>mvn package</code>, but it should work just fine in a single step build when you use <code>mvn install</code> or <code>mvn deploy</code>. Just a quick note. In one of our large projects we have a wrapper over junit&#39;s <code>TestBase</code> and it&#39;s located in <code>src&#47;main</code> which I don&#39;t consider to be a good idea either."
